      {l:"Outcome", t:"Success. Interceptors now account for a significant share of Geran kills per attack. The reason it held: radar cueing plus AI terminal guidance solved operator saturation (hundreds of drones a night) and link jamming at once \u2014 the AI guidance continues even when the operator's RF link is cut."}
