      {l:"Outcome", t:"Success for Ukraine, and a clear warning for us: bridge repair and route reconstitution under active drone observation are not viable \u2014 Russia could not repair Chonhar under repeated strike cycles. Observable, predictable engineer tasks (road repair, bridge reconstitution, obstacle clearing) face the same targeting logic as supply convoys."}
